name: Wine rack 3.0 walnut

Designed and made in Vancouver, BC.

name: VITO clear
description:
Versatile design that can be used as a
stool, side table and modules can be
arrange as a coffee table.

Red Oak solid hardwood
Mortise and tenon joinery.

Finish: semi-satin natural. 
Finishes are based on natural vegetable
oils and waxes.

Dimensions: L:18 D:16 H:17 inches

Made to order. 
Allow two weeks for fabrication + 2 weeks for shipping with tracking number.
